replies.body:
heart of iron is the name of the buff you get upon using the elixir of iron I believe.

 {{item:2138}} 

Also as far as I know, from around patch 6.8, elixir of iron has been inconsistent (generally nothing shows up but every once in a while some weird interaction goes wrong and elixir ends up not providing tenacity) in it's tenacity, especially the interactions with fear, root and grounded effects. The problems with tenacity and slow/stun/poly-morph interactions are interesting though since it appears to be working partially.
